        "Data": [
          "<h1>Applies To</h1>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>ASP.NET 4.0</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <h1>What to Do</h1>\r\n  <p>Perform authentication on the server by using ASP.NET forms authentication.</p>\r\n  <h1>Why</h1>\r\n  <p>Perform authentication on the server to make it harder for an attacker to bypass authentication controls. It is trivial to bypass client-side web authentication because the user can edit client-side scripts.</p>\r\n  <h1>When</h1>\r\n  <p>Use server-side authentication in all web applications that use authentication.</p>\r\n  <h1>How</h1>\r\n  <p>To use forms authentication, enable and configure the following section in <em>Web.config</em>:</p>\r\n  <pre>&lt;system.web&gt;<br />&nbsp; &lt;authentication mode=\"Forms\"&gt;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ...<br />&nbsp; &lt;/authentication&gt;<br />&lt;/system.web&gt;</pre>\r\n  <br />"
